EN: I forgot to bring my bank card to the store.
ZH: 请记得在取款机上插入银行卡。
EN: Please remember to insert your bank card at the ATM.
ZH: 我的银行卡被盗刷了，我得尽快联系银行。
EN: My bank card was skimmed, I need to contact the bank as soon as possible.
ZH: 如果你的银行卡丢了，赶快挂失。
EN: If your bank card is lost, report it as soon as possible.
ZH: 他的银行卡已经过期了，需要去银行换新的。
EN: His bank card has expired and needs to be replaced at the bank.
ZH: 确保在取款机上输入正确的银行卡密码。
EN: Make sure to enter the correct bank card PIN at the ATM.
ZH: 我的银行卡被吞了，我得去银行解决。
EN: My bank card got stuck in the machine, I need to go to the bank to resolve it.
ZH: 我的银行卡在中国不能用，需要开通国际支付功能。
EN: My bank card cannot be used in China, I need to activate international payment.
ZH: 记住不要把银行卡和密码放在一起。
EN: Remember not to keep your bank card and PIN together.
ZH: 没有银行卡，我们只能用现金支付。
EN: Without a bank card, we can only pay in cash.
