EN: Bank cards are an indispensable part of modern life.
ZH: 孩子们越来越晚用银行卡来支付开销。
EN: Children are using bank cards to pay for expenses later and later.
ZH: 老年人可能更喜欢用现金而不是银行卡。
EN: Elderly people may prefer to use cash rather than bank cards.
ZH: 在国外旅行时，银行卡是非常重要的。
EN: Bank cards are essential when traveling abroad.
ZH: 他的银行卡上有一笔未授权的交易。
EN: There is an unauthorized transaction on his bank card.
ZH: 银行卡被锁定后，需要去银行解锁。
EN: After the bank card is locked, you need to go to the bank to unlock it.
ZH: 请勿透露银行卡密码给他人。
EN: Do not disclose your bank card PIN to others.
ZH: 使用银行卡在线购物时，请确保网站的安全性。
EN: When using your bank card for online shopping, make sure the website is secure.
ZH: 我的银行卡上有一笔可疑的交易需要核实。
EN: There is a suspicious transaction on my bank card that needs to be verified.
